emained in both components for K1 at SUTHERLAND, in the in-phase component for M2 at CANBERRA and in the out-phase component for M2 at SYOWA. These residuals mean that there is a room for improvement in the estimation of ocean loading effect and/or the determination of calibration factors at these sites.},
