n those previously detected on the Jason-1 USO with a factor>10. The swept material used by manufacturers for the Jason-2 quartz oscillator has such properties to avoid non-linear effects >1-2{\textperiodcentered}10-12, (iii) the model is available at 1min or less over the Jason-2 mission, with a level of consistency of 5{\textperiodcentered}10-13, which is the average RMS of the post-fit residuals.},
