M3 and GOCO03S model do not have this phenomenon. The gravity model GOCO03S with combined CHAMP, GRACE and GOCE observations almost have no improvement in ACC estimate when compared with GOCE-TIM3 results, while the RMS of GOCO03S is a little larger than the GOCE-TIM3 results. {\textcopyright} 2013 Elsevier Ltd.},
